WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.279
Good morning, everybody! I just wanted

00:00:02.340 --> 00:00:08.219
to come on today and show you—we've

00:00:05.279 --> 00:00:10.200
worked so hard, my son did, from

00:00:08.220 --> 00:00:13.200
my memory of the flag.

00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:15.899
Everybody was asking us, "What does the

00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:18.180
Antichrist flag look like?"I told my son

00:00:15.900 --> 00:00:21.000
how it looked and he designed it.

00:00:18.180 --> 00:00:22.619
I'm excited to show you.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.080
I know it's something that's dark and

00:00:22.619 --> 00:00:27.480
very serious, but it's

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:29.939
something that came from my

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:32.099
memory of when I went to the Tribulation.

00:00:29.939 --> 00:00:34.860
This was ten years

00:00:32.098 --> 00:00:37.680
ago, almost ten

00:00:34.860 --> 00:00:40.440
years, so I was

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:42.540
excited to be able to finally get

00:00:40.440 --> 00:00:47.160
something that I've had inside of me

00:00:42.540 --> 00:00:49.200
this whole time out into reality. Here

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:52.078
you go; I'm going to show you—it's

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:55.620
going to be right here.

00:00:52.079 --> 00:01:00.840
The black represents ISIS,

00:00:55.620 --> 00:01:03.660
the white represents Al-Qaeda, and the

00:01:00.840 --> 00:01:09.000
green represents Palestine and Hamas.

00:01:03.660 --> 00:01:11.880
They're all on the flag as

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:12.479
a thank you for

00:01:12.479 --> 00:01:18.840
helping bring forth the Mahdi. There are

00:01:15.960 --> 00:01:21.600
gold sabers—these swords—and

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:23.280
you'll see these palms

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:25.259
behind it. I don't know what that

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:27.479
means or why it's there, but then there are

00:01:25.259 --> 00:01:30.960
stars at the top that go

00:01:27.479 --> 00:01:32.939
into an arch. That's the part I

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:35.699
had problems remembering—if there were

00:01:32.939 --> 00:01:37.258
five or seven. I don't

00:01:35.700 --> 00:01:39.360
remember all the way because I'm trying

00:01:37.259 --> 00:01:41.820
to remember everything, and like I

00:01:39.360 --> 00:01:43.680
said, it's kind of fuzzy. But I

00:01:41.820 --> 00:01:46.860
remember looking up and I could see

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:48.960
the flag, and there were

00:01:46.860 --> 00:01:51.840
stars on there in an arch

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:54.240
above the world. There's a globe in

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:56.939
the middle of the flag, in the

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:58.619
middle of the white.

00:01:56.939 --> 00:02:01.139
We worked on it really hard—my son did—from

00:01:58.619 --> 00:02:03.060
what I remembered in my

00:02:01.140 --> 00:02:06.180
mind of everything that I saw in the

00:02:03.060 --> 00:02:08.640
Tribulation. I'm trying to bring each

00:02:06.180 --> 00:02:11.580
thing that the Lord puts on my

00:02:08.639 --> 00:02:13.019
heart to show you all so that

00:02:11.580 --> 00:02:15.480
the people who are left here know

00:02:13.020 --> 00:02:18.540
what's coming. It shows

00:02:15.480 --> 00:02:21.720
you how close we are to Jesus

00:02:18.540 --> 00:02:23.840
coming to get us. I hope you're ready;

00:02:23.940 --> 00:02:28.680
the time is so short.

00:02:26.340 --> 00:02:30.360
Jesus Christ is about to come back and

00:02:28.680 --> 00:02:32.400
get us, and we're going to go home in the

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:34.739
Rapture. I know there are a lot of people

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:36.599
