00:03:28.980 --> 00:03:33.780
that

00:03:31.080 --> 00:03:37.200
so that I'm open-minded about things,

00:03:33.780 --> 00:03:40.319
but I just

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:42.179
think it's crazy. It's my

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:43.560
