00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:50.099
but I think you're wrong—so

00:03:46.019 --> 00:03:52.319
there. I just want to say to

00:03:50.099 --> 00:03:55.018
everybody, a lot of people did

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:57.179
